            <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
              <p>Hi there,<br>
I want to clarify if there is a possibility to set up alerts with a date as a reference. Or maybe a value from another column.<br>
We are doing a daily data load and I want to create an alarm in case if data was failed to load. So, I have a query that returns the load date and todayâ€™s date and I want to compare these values in an alert configuration. Can you please advise?</p>
