            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>I would do it this way:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-sql">SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN load_date = (current_date) THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END AS `match`
FROM some_table
LIMIT 1;
</code></pre>
<p>Then set your alert to evaluate whether <code>match == 1</code>.</p>
            </div>

